fulltitle: The Sound of Ben Webster: Part Two
description:
Our series on Ben Webster continues as we trace his career in the 1930's, from the classic sessions with Teddy Wilson and Billie Holiday, through the year with Cab Calloway, and then the breakthrough in Teddy Wilson;'s big band, which led directly to his famous years with Duke Ellington.
Hosted by NJMH Senior Scholar Loren Schoenberg
